title: The Adventure Zone: Live in Minneapolis!
description: Is it a dream? Maybe! Tres Horny Boys find themselves in the world’s deadliest cooking competition. They must battle delicious foes, entertain nutritious friends, endure tummy troubles, and impress the judges – or risk being forever labelled an idiot sandwich.
author: shows@themcelroy.family (Travis McElroy, Justin McElroy, Clint McElroy, Griffin McElroy)
